sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_075_2_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Install a certificate - CentralSystemRootCertificate
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: Central System supports Security profile 2 and/or 3

    CS->>CP: 1. InstallCertificate.req
    Note right of CS: certificateType = CentralSystemRootCertificate<br/>certificate = <Configured root certificate>

    CP-->>CS: 2. InstallCertificate.conf
    Note left of CP: status = Accepted

    CS->>CP: 3. GetInstalledCertificateIds.req
    Note right of CS: certificateType = CentralSystemRootCertificate

    CP-->>CS: 4. GetInstalledCertificateIds.conf
    Note left of CP: status = Accepted<br/>certificateHashData = <installed cert info>

    Note over CP,CS: Note: Must use a Root CA certificate<br/>for correct OCTT response
